  <div class="container">
    <div class="col justify-content-center">
      <h3>Minting</h3>
      <p>Minting is the act of registering/ validating an asset on a blockchain network, these assets are called NFTs (Non Fungible Tokens). OCM uses the XRPL network to successfully mint your NFToken on the XRPL. Follow the steps bellow to mint successfully on the XRPL.</p>
      <p>A fee of 2XRP is taken before you are able to complete the minting transaction. Pay the 2XRP fee then sign your minting transaction when the QR code changes.</p>
      <p>Head to your account page unlisteds to view your new NFToken.</p>
      <ol class="list-group list-group-numbered">
        <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start">
          <div class="ms-2 me-auto">
            <div class="fw-bold">Upload Image</div>
            Upload any image no larger than 10Mb.
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start">
          <div class="ms-2 me-auto">
            <div class="fw-bold">Metadata</div>
            Complete all information in the form below, this will be the metadata linked to your NFToken.
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start">
          <div class="ms-2 me-auto">
            <div class="fw-bold">Advanced Options</div>
            Refine how your NFToken will be minted on the XRPL with even more options.
          </div>
        </li>
      </ol>
      <p>For more information go <a href="https://xrpl.org/nftoken.html#nftoken" target="_blank">here.</a></p>
